[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1354[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The first action on every conversation turn is the same set of guardrails that the previous chapter 11 bots used: input safety screening, continuous emergency screening, identity classification (with vulnerable-populations awareness specific to recruitment), trial-state retrieval, and trial-context loading. The order matters. Emergency screening runs before anything else so that a patient saying "I'm having chest pain right now" is routed to 911 before the LLM sees the message; the LLM does not get to argue about a chest-pain message in a recruitment context.
