[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1356[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```python
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1357[0m:[38;5;10m[49m def receive_conversation_turn(*,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1358[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                                 session_id,
