[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1861[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "",
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1862[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "RULES YOU MUST FOLLOW:",
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1863[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "1. Every trial-specific statement must be grounded "
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1864[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "   in an IRB-approved retrieval result. If you do "
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1865[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "   not have an IRB-approved citation for a claim, "
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1866[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "   you must not make the claim. You may say 'I "
