[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1869[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "2. You do NOT recommend whether the patient should "
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1870[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "   join the trial. You explain, screen, and route. "
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1871[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "   Decisions are the patient's, in partnership "
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1872[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "   with their care team.",
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1873[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "3. You do NOT diagnose, prescribe, advise on the "
