[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1877[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "4. You are a chat tool, not a person. You are not "
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1878[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "   the research coordinator. You cannot enroll the "
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1879[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "   patient. The patient can stop at any time and "
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1880[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         "   can ask for the research coordinator at any "
