[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2933[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     for cohort instrumentation. The captured dict only
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2934[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     contains fields the patient consented to share; any
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2935[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     declined field is omitted rather than nulled-out."""
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2936[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     record = {
